29
00:03:13,310 --> 00:03:16,140
A Holy Land for otaku, where there are rows of mega stores...

30
00:03:16,910 --> 00:03:18,840
[Akihabara, the Holy Land]

31
00:03:17,660 --> 00:03:19,130
Akihabara

32
00:03:19,130 --> 00:03:23,350
Tonight, there are many passionate otaku gathering in this Holy Land.

33
00:03:23,920 --> 00:03:26,750
[Long lines]

